hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? metabothin 356 Avoid trying hair dryers or, even worse, microwaves. Time is your best friend in this scenario; the phone just has to dry out by itself. It’s not a bad idea, however, to place the device in something that can draw out the moisture, such as silica gel packets or uncooked rice. Still, you need to make sure that none of that stuff — especially those tiny grains of rice -- makes its way into the device.
